“We’ll wait until the eggs are done to wake him up.” Meera says.
“You’re making eggs too?” Bran says.
“Why do you sound so surprised?” Meera frowns.
“I don’t know, it’s just, I didn’t expect you to be the cooking type.” Bran admits. “You’re the ice cream for breakfast type. I know that, I’ve seen you eat ice cream for breakfast.”

summary: [SPOILERS] Gives me the chills
title: [SPOILERS] Gives me the chills
body:
I’ve recently been rewatching the series from beginning to end getting ready for the new season and I just finished S7E4. When Dany comes in with her dragon and says “dracarys” (sp) it gives me straight goosebumps. Every major event where this happens they play the same music and every time it gets me and sends chills down my spine, I love it so much.



Source: https://ift.tt/2OrLi3s
